---
title: Red Pepper and Goat's Cheese Rigatoni with Basil and Tarragon Pesto
description: When you think of pesto, you normally think of basil pesto. Well we think that’s a bit boring, so André’s gone a bit quirky here and added tarragon into the mix, along with walnuts instead of pine nuts. Trust us, you’ll never eat normal pesto again!
